  provinceImage3: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 355e09d80ed879041b6332c3086a82dd, type: 3}
  description: "C\xE0 Mau l\xE0 t\u1EC9nh n\u1EB1m \u1EDF c\u1EF1c Nam c\u1EE7a Vi\u1EC7t
    Nam, thu\u1ED9c v\xF9ng \u0110\u1ED3ng b\u1EB1ng s\xF4ng C\u1EEDu Long. N\u01A1i
    \u0111\xE2y n\u1ED5i ti\u1EBFng v\u1EDBi h\u1EC7 sinh th\xE1i r\u1EEBng ng\u1EADp
    m\u1EB7n phong ph\xFA v\xE0 v\xF9ng \u0111\u1EA5t m\u0169i thi\xEAng li\xEAng
    c\u1EE7a T\u1ED5 qu\u1ED1c t\u1EA1i M\u0169i C\xE0 Mau. C\xE0 Mau c\xF3 m\u1EA1ng
    l\u01B0\u1EDBi s\xF4ng ng\xF2i ch\u1EB1ng ch\u1ECBt, thu\u1EADn l\u1EE3i cho
    nu\xF4i tr\u1ED3ng v\xE0 \u0111\xE1nh b\u1EAFt th\u1EE7y s\u1EA3n, \u0111\u1EB7c
    bi\u1EC7t l\xE0 t\xF4m. Ngo\xE0i ra, t\u1EC9nh c\xF2n c\xF3 V\u01B0\u1EDDn qu\u1ED1c
    gia M\u0169i C\xE0 Mau \u2013 khu d\u1EF1 tr\u1EEF sinh quy\u1EC3n th\u1EBF gi\u1EDBi
    v\u1EDBi nhi\u1EC1u lo\xE0i \u0111\u1ED9ng th\u1EF1c v\u1EADt \u0111\u1EB7c tr\u01B0ng
    c\u1EE7a r\u1EEBng ng\u1EADp m\u1EB7n. C\xE0 Mau c\u0169ng mang \u0111\u1EADm
    n\xE9t v\u0103n h\xF3a s\xF4ng n\u01B0\u1EDBc v\xE0 con ng\u01B0\u1EDDi hi\u1EC1n
    h\xF2a, m\u1EBFn kh\xE1ch."
  desSatNhap: "T\u1EEB ng\xE0y 1 th\xE1ng 7 n\u0103m 2025, t\u1EC9nh C\xE0 Mau s\u1EBD
    s\xE1p nh\u1EADp v\u1EDBi t\u1EC9nh B\u1EA1c Li\xEAu, t\u1EA1o th\xE0nh m\u1ED9t
    t\u1EC9nh m\u1EDBi c\xF3 t\xEAn g\u1ECDi l\xE0 t\u1EC9nh C\xE0 Mau v\u1EDBi 64
    \u0111\u01A1n v\u1ECB h\xE0nh ch\xEDnh."
